git clone https://github.com/EricJMarti/inventory-hunter
cd inventory-hunter
docker pull ericjmarti/inventory-hunter:latest
./docker_run.bash -c ./config/amazon_IT_rtx_3070.yaml -a telegram -w https://api.telegram.org/bot{VOSTRA URL API TELEGRAM}/sendMessage -d chat_id {VOSTO ID CHAT}



Stop and remove all containers related to inventory-hunter
$ docker stop CONTAINER_NAME
$ docker rm CONTAINER_NAME